<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In answer to Salley, I believe Philip Marlowe&apos;s story chronology goes... 1. The Big Sleep (1939) 2. Farewell, My Lovely (1940) 3. The High Window (194<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In answer to Salley, I believe Philip Marlowe's story chronology goes... 1. The Big Sleep (1939) 2. Farewell, My Lovely (1940) 3. The High Window (1942) 4. The Lady in the Lake (1943) 5. The Little Sister (1949) 6. The Simple Art of Murder (1950) (short story collection) 7. The Long Goodbye (1953) 8. Playback (1958) 9. Poodle Springs (1988)* *Started 1958 by Chandler &amp; completed by Robert B. Parker. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
